"title": "8767: hypocrisy",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8767: hypocrisy",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An outward pretence masking an inner reality. Scripture condemns hypocrisy, especially in matters of faith. Believers should express their commitment to God in their words and their deeds, as well as in their inner motivation.</p>\n<h2>The origin of hypocrisy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:2\">HOS 10:2</a> <em>Israel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:22\">MRK 7:21–7:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a></p>\n<h2>The expression of hypocrisy</h2>\n<h3>Insincere motives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:2\">MAT 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5\">MAT 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:16\">MAT 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:7-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:7–15:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:18\">MAT 22:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:5-Matt23:7\">MAT 23:5–23:7</a></p>\n<h3>When deeds do not match words</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:7-Matt15:8\">MAT 15:7–15:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6\">MRK 7:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:24-Prov26:26\">PRO 26:24–26:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:8\">JER 9:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:2\">JER 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek33:31\">EZK 33:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:28\">MAT 23:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:17-Rom2:24\">ROM 2:17–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:14-Jas2:26\">JAS 2:14–2:26</a></p>\n<h3>A tendency to judge others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:5\">MAT 7:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:41\">LUK 6:41</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:1\">ROM 2:1</a></p>\n<h2>The alternative to hypocrisy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3-Ps24:4\">PSA 24:3–24:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps26:4\">PSA 26:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:2\">PSA 32:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:17\">JAS 3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:1-1Pet2:3\">1PE 2:1–2:3</a></p>\n<h2>Hypocrisy is not to be found in leaders</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:8-1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:8–28:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:6\">MAL 2:6</a> <em>the true priest</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:1-1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:1–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:8\">1TI 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:8\">TIT 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:1\">JAS 3:1</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of hypocrites</h2>\n<h3>Israel's leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:13\">JER 6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:8\">JER 8:8</a></p>\n<h3>The Pharisees</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:38-Mark12:40\">MRK 12:38–12:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:1-Matt23:32\">MAT 23:1–23:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:1-Luke12:2\">LUK 12:1–12:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:56\">LUK 12:56</a></p>\n<h3>Peter and Barnabas</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:12-Gal2:13\">GAL 2:12–2:13</a></strong> <em>By acting in this way, Peter was denying his own conviction that Gentiles could be saved by faith without having to submit to the law.</em></p>\n<h3>Many false teachers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:17-Rom16:18\">ROM 16:17–16:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:17\">PHP 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:2\">1TI 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:5\">2TI 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:16\">JUD 1:16</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those who did not practise hypocrisy</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:21-1Pet2:22\">1PE 2:21–2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44-John8:46\">JHN 8:44–8:46</a></p>\n<h3>Paul and his companions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:12\">2CO 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:17\">2CO 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:3-1Thess2:10\">1TH 2:3–2:10</a></p>",
